# Multizonal Transdimensional Inversion
# SETTINGS - Inversion (keep lines order including comments)
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEPTH: min_depth [m] (>0.0 due to Log-domain), max_depth of the profile [m]
0.5  300.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ZONES: number of dept-zones (=1 for single-zonal inversion)
1
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ZONES: thicknesses of dept-zones [m] (in row, the last is half-space -> 0.0)
0.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# S-WAVE VELOCITY: minimum and maximum thresholds [m/s] (one line per zone)
50.0  3000.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# P-WAVE VELOCITY: minimum and maximum thresholds [m/s] (one line per zone)
70.0  6000.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DENSITY: minimum and maximum [kg/m^3] (1 line per zone, min=max -> fixed Rho)
2000.0  3000.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# POISSON's RATIO: minimum and maximum (one line per zone, min=max -> fixed nu)
0.2  0.4
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MCMC Gaussian steps: Vs, Vp, Rho (one line per zone, 1sigma in resp. units)
5.0  10.0  20.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MCMC Gaussian steps: Log-depth domain (single value, 1sigma in ln([m]) units)
0.02
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# INVERSE VELOCITY GRADIENT: max. depth [m] (0.0 -> no low-velocity zones)
0.0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MCMC settings: Chains, Burn-in steps, Total steps (recomm. [20 5000 40000])
20 5000 40000
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# WORKING DIRECTORY (max. 80 chars, no whitespace, no special characters)
./inv/
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DIMENSIONS: Total maximal number of the Voronoi nuclei (recomm. 30)
30
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DIMENSIONS: Transdimensional proposal probability (<0.45, P_birth=P_death)
0.05
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EXPERT SWITCH: explore_prior, negative_timeout, group_velocity, initial_model
0  0  0  0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional_A: Number of fixed number of layers (non-transdimensional inversion)
0
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional_B: Number of fixed Voronoi nuclei (non-transdimensional inversion)
0
# Optional_B: Fixed Voronoi nuclei: Depth [m], Vs [m/s], Vp [m/s], Rho [kg/m^3]
4 -1 -1 -1
6 -1 -1 -1
56 -1 -1 -1
